<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="h-auto col-md-10 offset-md-1">
      <div class="header-card">
        <div class="row justify-content-between align-items-center">
          <div class="col-3">
            <div class="avatar">
              <img src="https://bootdey.com/img/Content/avatar/avatar2.png" class="d-block w-100">
              <div>
                <img src="https://bootdey.com/img/Content/avatar/avatar6.png" alt="" class="avatarSub">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col align-self-end">
            <div class="col">
              <span class="nomePersonagem">Nome do Personagem</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body body">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-3">
            <div class="card gedf-card jogador">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Jogador Da Mesa:</h5>
                <h6>Mesa de teste Jogada</h6>
                <h5>Evolução na matéria</h5>
                <div class="progress">
                  <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated"
                          role="progressbar" style="width: 25%" aria-valuenow="25"
                          aria-valuemin="0" aria-valuemax="100">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <h5>Ficha do Personagem</h5>
                <div class="pdf">
                  <div class="action" id="orange">
                    <h3>
                      <img src="<%= image_url('Pdf.svg') %>" alt="">
                    </h3>
                    <span>Anexo PDF</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <%#   POST   %>
          <div class="col-md-9 gedf-main">
            <div class="card gedf-card post">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-10">
                    <div class="user">
                      <img src="https://bootdey.com/img/Content/avatar/avatar6.png" alt="" />
                      <div class="user-info">
                        <h5>NOME DO ALUNO FULANO</h5>
                        <small>Personagem Ciclano</small>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-2">
                    <div class="text-muted h7 mb-2 text-right">
                      <span class="time">10 min ago</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col">
                    <p class="card-text" id="content">
                      when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quo recusandae nulla remeos ipsa.
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="card-footer card-footer-profile">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col links">
                    <a href="#" >
                      <img src="<%= image_url('Youtube.svg') %>" alt="">
                      <span>Youtube</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
